src.cross_cutting_infrastrucuture.contra.description:
Decorator to explicitly declare that a function or class relies on a specific contract.
This serves as documentation and allows for static analysis of contract dependencies.

Usage:
    @uses_contract(RoutingContract)
    def my_function():
        ...

src.cross_cutting_infrastrucuture.capaz_.description:
Get layer compatibility matrix showing which layers can coexist.

Returns:
    Nested dict: {layer1: {layer2: compatible_bool}}
